  "text": "Hand crafted systems such as [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] use transformation rules that encode morphological changes as well as deletions, re-orderings, substitutions and sentence splitting, and can handle voice change correctly. However, hand crafted systems are limited in scope to syntactic simplification as there are too many lexico-syntactic and lexical simplifications to enumerate manually.",
